      "id": 22,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 66
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Stack layout\n- **Router** (job `router`): Cursor/OpenAI clients hit **port 4001**; Prometheus scrapes **`/metrics`** here \u2014 primary SLO panels above.\n- **Ollama** (job `ollama`): **`up`** needs a recent Ollama build with **`GET /metrics`** on **11434**. If **Ollama scrape up** is **0**, run `curl -sS http://localhost:11434/metrics | head` on the host and **`task update`** to refresh the image.\n- Panels query **`ollama_model_requests_total`** *or* **`requests_total`** \u2014 depending on your Ollama version one series may be empty.\n\n### Useful commands\n```bash\ntask status\ncurl -s http://localhost:9090/api/v1/targets | python3 -m json.tool   # scrape status\ndocker logs ollama-router --tail 80\n```\n"
      }
